Vendored prebuilt WebAssembly HTMLRewriter engine.

Source: html-rewriter-wasm 0.4.1 (https://github.com/mrbbot/html-rewriter-wasm),
the prebuilt `dist/` artifacts (html_rewriter.js, asyncify.js,
html_rewriter_bg.wasm). The .wasm is lol-html (https://github.com/cloudflare/lol-html)
compiled to WebAssembly with Binaryen's Asyncify pass, which is what gives the
engine full async-handler support (the WASM stack is unwound while a handler
Promise resolves, then rewound to continue the transform).

Both html-rewriter-wasm and lol-html are BSD 3-Clause licensed.

